description: Rarely available, front facing 1BD/1.5BA loft at 25 Channel Center, an elevator building with concierge service. Enjoy access to all of the shopping, dining and entertainment in Fort Point/Seaport and South Boston! This condo boasts dramatic floor to ceiling windows that overlook downtown Boston and Fort Point Channel, soaring high ceilings that bring in ample sunlight, and is jaw dropping upon entering. This open concept loft residence features a contemporary kitchen with brand new counters, gas cooking which overlooks the ample living/dining room. There is also a powder room on this floor. Upstairs, the primary suite is spacious with a walk in closet and an en suite bathroom along with the washer/dryer. The hardwood floors were just refinished on the lower level and there is hardwood flooring throughout. To top it off there is 1 direct access garage parking space.
